title: U.S. State Boundaries Region 8 (CO MO ND SD UT and WY), USA, 2008
name: U.S. State Boundaries Region 8 (CO MO ND SD UT and WY), USA, 2008
description:
Abstract: The State Boundary with Detailed Shorelines database was created using TIGER/LINE 2000 shapefile data gathered from ESRI's Geography Network.  The individual county shapefiles were processed into Arc/Info coverages and then appended together to create complete state coverages.  RITA/BTS Hydrographic data was integrated to create detailed shorelines.
    Purpose: The United States State Boundaries database is a geographic database of state political boundaries.  The database includes boundaries for all 50 states plus Puerto Rico and Washington D.C.
